Credit Line Hybrid Program Up to 150K in Unsecured No-Doc Credit Cards for Your Business Even When Banks Say “NO”

Get Started

(Flexible, Reliable Solution for Business Funding)

The Credit Line Hybrid is designed to help clients get funding based strictly on personal credit quality. Our lenders will not ask for financials, bank statements, business plans, resumes, or any of the other burdensome document requests that most conventional lenders demand.

This is as close to a “no-doc” program as you can get with business funding. And the best part is that you can even get approval with introductory rates as low as 0% giving this program the best terms in the country.

How to Qualify for Funding With the Credit Line Hybrid

Below are the requirements to qualify for Credit Line Hybrid by either you or a Credit Partner who has at least 10% ownership in the business:

700+ credit score with all three consumer credit bureaus
No more than 4 unsecured accounts open in the past 12 months
Credit Card 3 Years old with a $5,000+ limit (Must be a primary card)
No more than 4-6 inquiries per bureau in the last 6 months- preferably less
Minimum of two (2) open revolving account with a year and a half of good payment history
No bankruptcies within the past 7 years
Under 40% utilization on all revolving accounts
No open (unpaid) collections, liens or judgments
This program does require a Personal Guarantee from you or your credit partner if you use one. NO AUTHORIZED USER ACCOUNTS for qualification.

Terms That Can’t Be Beat

This program offers some of the best terms around, including interest rates as low as 0% interest for 6 to 18 months. Interest rates vary with each credit line.

How Much Does It Cost?

There is a one time Success Fee of 9.9% that is due after you have received access to your credit lines. If you don't get approved - you don't pay. Best of all, you can use your new 0% credit lines to pay the success fee.
